definition: Qishan County in Baoji 寶雞|宝鸡[Bao3 ji1], Shaanxi
surname Qi/also used in place names
mountain/hill/anything that resembles a mountain/CL:座[zuo4]/bundled straw in which silkworms spin cocoons/gable

sentences.english: Qishan County lies on the west of Fufeng County.
sentences.chinese: 岐山縣位於扶風縣的西面。
